the next section. Send a welcome message. <br>
<input type=radio name=func value="subscribe-set-nowelcome"> 
Add subscribers using the addresses and settings in
the next section. <b>Do not</b> send a welcome message.<br>
<input type=radio name=func value="unsubscribe"> 
Remove subscribers using the addresses in the large box
in the next section of this form.
